Here are some additional reputable websites that provide information on the science behind electrotherapy:

1. National Center for Biotechnology Information (NCBI): <https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/>
2. Mayo Clinic: <https://www.mayoclinic.org/>
3. American Physical Therapy Association (APTA): <https://www.apta.org/>
4. MedlinePlus: <https://medlineplus.gov/>
5. National Institute of Neurological Disorders and Stroke (NINDS): <https://www.ninds.nih.gov/>
